  <section class="container">
    <div class="columns features">
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-image has-text-centered">
              <i class="fa fa-connectdevelop"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Decentralised </h4>
              <p>A decentralised architecture ensures distributed authority, power. Appropriate data is encrypted and stored in fragments among peer devices.<br>P2P ensures trust with faster data transfer rates.</p>
              <p><a href="https://medium.com/@petkanics/the-benefits-of-decentralization-88a0b5d0fd39" target="_blank">The Benefits of Decentralization</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-image has-text-centered">
              <i class="fa fa-user-secret"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="content">
              <h4>End-to-end encrypted</h4>
              <p>End to end cryptosystem implemented with Elliptic Curve Cryptography (ECC-Curve25519) and Advanced Encryption Standard(AES-256) ensures the message reaches only the intended audience.<br><!--Data is in form of ciphertext both at rest and in transit.<br>--><b>This means neither centralised system administrators who have physical access nor external prying eyes get hold of your sensitive data.</b></p>
              <p><a href="http://bitwiseshiftleft.github.io/sjcl/">Stanford Javascript Crypto Library</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-image has-text-centered">
              <i class="fa fa-github"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="content">
              <h4>The love of Open-Source  </h4>
              <p>This open is open-sourced, all the code running behind is on <a href="https://github.com/tameeshB/sockChat">GitHub.</a><br>
                Being open source, the architecture and all []s make the application transparent and hence reliable.
                <br>Feel free to join in, put in a PR or two or rather fork it and build your own version!</p>
                This project is licensed under GNU General Public License v2.0.
              <p><a href="https://github.com/tameeshB/sockChat">GitHub repo</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/tameeshB/sockChat/blob/master/LICENSE.md">LICENSE.md</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

